        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "This once again raises the urgency of re-using the vimscript filesystem functions, to implement parts of `vim.fs` (where applicable). Reimplementing stuff from whole-cloth in `vim.fs` makes no sense, if there is already an equivalent builtin such as `fnamemodify()`.",
            "created_at": "2026-02-27T11:41:00Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/37698#issuecomment-3972480028",
